Comment: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:44.60,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:53.11,Default,Reporter A,0,0,0,,Excuse me.{NOTE:あ、ちょっと失礼します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:54.99,Default,Reporter A,0,0,0,,Please answer some questions.{NOTE:Xお願いします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:55.90,Default,Reporter B,0,0,0,,Inokuma-san.{NOTE:猪野熊さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:02:00.45,Default,Reporter B,0,0,0,,There were various problems in the training camp at Miyazaki, but how is All-Japan team doing now?{NOTE:宮崎の合宿は色々問題もあったようですが、どうです？オールジャパンの調子は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:03.74,Default,Reporter A,0,0,0,,How far do you think you can go at the world championships?{NOTE:席は相手に戦ってどの辺まで行けると思いますか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:06.33,Default,Reporter B,0,0,0,,It will be a success if we could reach the quarterfinals.{NOTE:準々決勝まで行けるは先ず成功でしょうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:08.08,Default,Reporter B,0,0,0,,What are your expectations, coach?{NOTE:そう言うはどうです、コーチ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:13.55,Default,Reporter A,0,0,0,,We can't think you're aiming for the first place, can we?{NOTE:それともまさか優勝を狙ってるとは考えていないでしょうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:15.05,Default,Reporter A,0,0,0,,How about that?{NOTE:それはどうでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:16.72,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,We're aiming for it.{NOTE:考えています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:17.84,Default,Reporter B,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:21.30,Default,Reporter A,0,0,0,,Then do you have a secret strategy to win with the Soviet Union?{NOTE:それでは世界一のソ連に勝つ秘策があるんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:22.72,Default,Reporter A,0,0,0,,What kind of strategy is it?{NOTE:どんな作戦です？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:23.81,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,My strategy…{NOTE:それは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:27.64,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,…lies in the individual players' results from the training camp.{NOTE:選手一人一人の合宿の成果そのものは作戦でありXです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:29.14,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,It's the ten people over there.{NOTE:あそこにいる十人の。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:31.73,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,Hey, Kozue—{NOTE:ね、こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:33.40,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It'll be all right, mom.{NOTE:ママ、大丈夫よもう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:36.69,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. You don't worry about me, mom.{NOTE:よく分かってるんだから、ね、ママ心配何かしないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:38.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Exactly.{NOTE:そうなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:40.49,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,My dad's all like…{NOTE:ん、私のパパも先から…}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:43.41,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,…"don't each too much" and "be sure to wake up early".{NOTE:…食べ過ぎないようにとかさ、ねXXしちゃいけないとかさ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:45.83,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,He treats me like preschooler.{NOTE:…XX小学生であるまいし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:50.50,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– But Midori…\N– A bird must leave its nest some day.{NOTE:—がっしかし、みどり。\\N—雛鳥はいつかは親鳥の巣を飛び立っていくのですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:51.33,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,Right, mama?{NOTE:ね、ママ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:52.42,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,It's for the best.{NOTE:これでいいんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:53.25,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Exactly.{NOTE:そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:55.92,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Please have a bit more faith in us.{NOTE:もっと私達を信じてちょうだい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.63,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,I see you're both pretty confident.{NOTE:二人共自身たっぷりだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:02:58.84,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,But the world is vast.{NOTE:でも世界は広いんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.55,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,Don't get lost in that world.{NOTE:井の中の蛙に成るなよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:02.14,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Don't say weird things.{NOTE:変な事言わないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:04.14,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,This time is different.{NOTE:今度前の時が違うんだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:05.14,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Right, Kozue?{NOTE:ね、こずえ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:08.48,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yep. We've trained so hard.{NOTE:え。あれだけのハードトレーニングを乗り切ったんですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll put up a good fight.{NOTE:きっと全力を出し切ってくるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:12.27,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Yep. That's the spirit.{NOTE:そうよ。そうこなくちゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:13.73,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:ん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:19.03,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,The nicest thing about this trip is that\NI won't see you Kyūshū boys for a while.{NOTE:今度帰ってきたら、九州男児九州男児XXXせんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.49,Default,Kakinouchi's friend,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah, heh.{NOTE:え？えへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.16,Default,Kakinouchi's friend,0,0,0,,That's tough.{NOTE:あ、これは参った仕事な。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:26.45,Default,Miyatsu,0,0,0,,I'm so happy that I can play. I'll do my best.{NOTE:気持ちよかったXX頑張ってよかったXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:29.58,Default,Yoshimura's teacher,0,0,0,,Meihou Academy will root for you.{NOTE:明方学園の全部は期待してるからね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:30.62,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,Thanks.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:32.79,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,You made it, Noda! Hooray!{NOTE:野田XXX万歳！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.33,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Hooray!\N– Hooray!{NOTE:—万歳！\\N—万歳！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:35.79,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.{NOTE:任しておいて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:38.67,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,Foreigners don't stand a chance against us.{NOTE:外人何か軽すぎてXX人だよな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:40.51,Default,Ootsuki,0,0,0,,There will be only Americans here.{NOTE:アメリカ人ばかりだとね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.38,Default,Ootsuki,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'll be able to talk with them?{NOTE:言葉分かるだろうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:44.47,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,Professor, I'm anxious.{NOTE:先生。私心配なんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:47.43,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,I've practiced with all I've got, but I feel like it wasn't enough.{NOTE:精一杯練習したつもりでも、未だ何か足りないような。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:48.85,Default,Mishima's teacher,0,0,0,,That's no good.{NOTE:嫌、いかんいかんいかん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:53.27,Default,Mishima's teacher,0,0,0,,Stop thinking like that. Don't forget that you were chosen as part of the All Japan team.{NOTE:そんな弱気は禁物じゃ。オールジャパンに選ばれたと言う栄養を忘れんで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:54.44,Default,Mishima's teacher,0,0,0,,You need to work hard.{NOTE:しっかり頑張るんじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:55.31,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,Yes.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:57.77,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,Oh?{NOTE:あら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:02.07,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,Professor, excuse me for a moment.{NOTE:先生ちょっとごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:05.74,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,Shirakawa-san.{NOTE:白河さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.12,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,Kitami-san.{NOTE:北見さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:08.29,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,Thank you.{NOTE:有難う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:09.83,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,You came here to see me off?{NOTE:見送りに来てくれたな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:12.58,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,Everyone will be thrilled to see you. I'll go let them know.{NOTE:皆も喜ぶわ。私知らせてくる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.29,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,You girls…{NOTE:あなた達…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:20.84,Default,Shirakawa,0,0,0,,We wanted to see you off here for a long time.{NOTE:ここでずっと見送りたいんだ、私達。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:23.13,Default,Kitami,0,0,0,,We're weak.{NOTE:私達負け犬よ。弱虫なのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:27.18,Default,Kitami,0,0,0,,No matter how much we regret it, nothing changes that we've dropped out.{NOTE:今成って脱落した事、いくら後悔しても始まらないけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.94,Default,Kitami,0,0,0,,Mishima-san, do your best in our place.{NOTE:三島さん、私達の分も頑張ってきてね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:39.94,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,I will.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:40.94,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,You can count on me.{NOTE:分かったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:42.44,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.{NOTE:きっとやる。頑張る。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.32,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,– Mishima-san!\N– Mishima-san!{NOTE:—三島さん！\\N—三島さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:46.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah, it's professor Hongou.{NOTE:あ、本郷先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:47.53,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Professor.{NOTE:先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:48.62,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Hey.{NOTE:よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:50.49,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Ayuhara, Hayakawa.{NOTE:鮎原、早川。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:51.95,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,– Sir.\N– Sir.{NOTE:—はい。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:54.58,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I don't have anything particular to say to you.{NOTE:や。別に改まって言うこともない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:56.71,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I believe in you.{NOTE:先生はお前達を信じているからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:58.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:01.34,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Ah, what's this?{NOTE:あら、これは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:07.51,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,It's the ball we used during the All-Japan championships.{NOTE:我々が日本選手権で優勝した時のボールだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:12.14,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Take it. It holds memories and dreams of the whole Fujimi Academy volleyball team.{NOTE:ほら。富士見学園バレーチーム全員の色々な思い出と祈りが狙っている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:18.06,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,What's that? Pay attention!{NOTE:どうした？行くぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:27.86,Default,Oohara,0,0,0,,Get a grip!{NOTE:しっかり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:36.62,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Forgive me.{NOTE:許してね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.00,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,Professor!{NOTE:先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:55.64,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,It bears the hope of the ones left behind.{NOTE:後に残った者たちの希望だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:57.35,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Hold onto this ball.{NOTE:そのボールを持っていてくれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:57.98,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yes sir.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:00.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We'll make it our mascot and do our best.{NOTE:私達のマスコットにして頑張ります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.06,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Good.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:01.94,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I expect a lot from you.{NOTE:期待しているぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:02.90,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Hongou!{NOTE:本郷！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:03.44,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Hm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.24,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Inokuma.{NOTE:お、猪野熊。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.70,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Take care of Ayuhara and the team.{NOTE:鮎原たちを頼む。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:10.37,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Got it.{NOTE:分かった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.87,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I pray from the bottom of my heart for your success.{NOTE:心からからお前の健闘を祈る。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:15.62,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Thank you.{NOTE:有難う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:23.50,Default,Sanjou's stepmom,0,0,0,,Ah, it's your coach, isn't it?{NOTE:あら、コーチの先生ですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.21,Default,Sanjou's stepmom,0,0,0,,I'll go say hello to him.{NOTE:ちょっとご挨拶してきましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.51,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,– L-Let him be.\N– Eh?{NOTE:—いいのよ。\\N—え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:27.84,Default,Sanjou's stepmom,0,0,0,,What's wrong?{NOTE:だって、お前…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:28.80,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,Everything's fine.{NOTE:大丈夫よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.55,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,Michiru isn't alone.{NOTE:美智留一人じゃないんだもん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:35.18,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,Beyond that, I have something to tell you when I come back from America.{NOTE:それより私アメリカから帰ってきたらパパとママにお話ししたいことがあるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.98,Default,Sanjou's stepdad,0,0,0,,What do you want to tell us?{NOTE:話？どんな事だ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.81,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,I think it'll surprise you.{NOTE:パパもママもきっとビックリすると思うわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:46.94,Default,Reporter A,0,0,0,,Coach Inokuma is full of confidence.{NOTE:猪野熊コーチは自信たっぷりのようですが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:48.07,Default,Reporter A,0,0,0,,What about you?{NOTE:あなた方としては？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.32,Default,Reporter A,0,0,0,,Think you can win?{NOTE:自信はありますか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.16,Default,Reporter A,0,0,0,,– How is it?\N– Ah.{NOTE:—どうです？\\N—あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I do.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.37,Default,Reporter A,0,0,0,,Can you win with the Soviet Union?{NOTE:ソ連には勝てますか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:54.53,Default,Reporter B,0,0,0,,What about United States?{NOTE:アメリカには？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:57.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yes. We will do our utmost.{NOTE:え。精一杯遣ります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:59.04,Default,Reporter C,0,0,0,,Can you really win?{NOTE:勝てる？大丈夫？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.71,Default,Reporter B,0,0,0,,Your opponents are strong.{NOTE:敵も強いよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:01.88,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We're well aware of it.{NOTE:分かっています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:03.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We'll simply do our best.{NOTE:全力を尽くすだけです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:06.84,Default,Reporter A,0,0,0,,Aw, that's rather weak statement.{NOTE:おや、おや。ちょっと頼りないね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:07.84,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,We'll win.{NOTE:勝ちます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.34,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,We'll win for sure!{NOTE:絶対に勝ちます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.30,Default,Reporter C,0,0,0,,Now we're talking.{NOTE:はは、これは強きだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.39,Default,Reporter C,0,0,0,,Can you promise me victory?{NOTE:俺らに約束できますかね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:14.26,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,We can.{NOTE:できます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:17.85,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I swear by that red sun.{NOTE:あの日の丸にかけて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.20,Default,Reporter C,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, what about you?{NOTE:鮎原さんはどうです？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Very well. We promise you.{NOTE:はい。お約束します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:42.21,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1\fad(0,700)}The 14 o'clock flight to the New York via Honolulu will be departing soon.{NOTE:14時発ホノルル経由ニューヨーク行きはまもなく出発致します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:45.46,Default,Crowd,0,0,0,,– Good luck!\N– Do your best, Ayuhara-san!{NOTE:—ガンバレよ！\\N—頑張ってよ！鮎原さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:48.21,Default,Crowd,0,0,0,,{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:49.76,Default,Crowd,0,0,0,,{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:52.88,Default,Crowd,0,0,0,,{NOTE:—頑張って！\\N—XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:18.41,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Hey, check it out. It's speeding up.{NOTE:おい見ろ。いよいよ離陸だぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.25,Default,Mishima's teacher,0,0,0,,Mishima, good luck!{NOTE:三島！頑張るだと！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.96,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Do your best.\N– Take it easy.{NOTE:—頑張ってね。\\N—しっかりね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:33.09,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, girls.{NOTE:皆、頼むんだぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:44.81,Default,Kakinouchi's friend,0,0,0,,You better show them, Kyūshū's princess!{NOTE:頑張らない緩さんぞ、九州撫子！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:55.45,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,Good luck.{NOTE:頑張れよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:57.62,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,Next time you'll visit Haneda…{NOTE:君達が今度羽田降りるとき。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:09:00.37,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,…will we be rejoicing, or will we be struck with sadness?{NOTE:笑いながら降りられるか泣き顔で追い出すか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:02.83,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,Everything depends on the games to come.{NOTE:それは全てこれからの試合に勝っているんだぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:06.71,Alternative,Reporter A,0,0,0,,Can you win with the Soviet Union?{NOTE:ソ連には勝てますか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:07.88,Alternative,Reporter A,0,0,0,,What about United States?{NOTE:アメリカには？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:08.84,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We'll do our utmost.{NOTE:精一杯遣ります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.21,Alternative,Reporter A,0,0,0,,Can you really win?{NOTE:勝てる？大丈夫？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:11.96,Alternative,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Your opponents are strong.\N– We're well aware of it.{NOTE:—敵も強いよ。\\N—分かってます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:14.09,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We'll simply do our best.{NOTE:全力を尽くすだけです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:15.59,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:19.60,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I'll be training my and Borchinskaya's cross toss to its limits.{NOTE:私は十字トスとボルチンスカヤをさらに(XX・期待します)。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:22.56,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for your letter of challenge.{NOTE:そしてあなたの挑戦を待っています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:40.58,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Borchinskaya's killer spike.{NOTE:ボルチンスカヤの殺人スパイク。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.64,Default,Ootsuki,0,0,0,,Ah, it's New York!{NOTE:あ、ニューヨークよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.31,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Wah!\N– Eh!?{NOTE:—わ！\\N—え！？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:13.53,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.25,Default,Ootsuki,0,0,0,,We're in America!{NOTE:ここがアメリカだとね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:32.75,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,– I'll take lots of pictures.\N– My heart's racing!{NOTE:—写真を撮ろう、たっぷり。\\N—胸がワクワク行っちゃうわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:35.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I wonder if the Soviet team is already here.{NOTE:ソ連チームもう来てるかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:35.51,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Hm?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:36.67,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Did you say something?{NOTE:何か言った？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:38.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Nothing.{NOTE:何も。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:50.56,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Here is the Central Gym.{NOTE:ここはセントラル体育館。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:54.44,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Here the fierce battle is going to start the day after tomorrow and last for one week.{NOTE:ここであさってから一週間過酷XXを選手との激戦が始まる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:56.65,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Amazing. We'll be playing here.{NOTE:すごいわ、ここで試合をするのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:59.40,Default,Miyatsu,0,0,0,,It'll host matches between teams from 16 countries.{NOTE:それも十六国のチームと戦うんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:01.03,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,How far can we go?{NOTE:どこまでやれるか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:03.53,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,The time to challenge the world has finally come.{NOTE:いよいよ世界に挑戦する時が来たわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.33,Default,Miyatsu,0,0,0,,I'm all itching to play.{NOTE:腕がムズムズしてきた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:29.14,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.56,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Ah, Kozue.{NOTE:あ、こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:33.40,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah? S-Sir.{NOTE:は？あ、は、はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:34.81,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Gather everyone.{NOTE:皆を集合させてくれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:36.61,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,We're going to the hotel.{NOTE:かれから宿舎のホテルへ行く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:37.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yes sir.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:41.07,Default,Ootsuki,0,0,0,,Wow, so nice.{NOTE:わ、おっ魂消た。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.28,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,It's pretty luxurious.{NOTE:豪勢なもんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:44.99,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,It's completely different from the Miyazaki training camp.{NOTE:宮崎の合宿ともお違いだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:47.54,Default,Miyatsu,0,0,0,,Wow, it's first time I have such a big bed.{NOTE:わ、私こんなの初めてだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:50.00,Default,Miyatsu,0,0,0,,I feel like a princess in a castle.{NOTE:まるでお城のお姫様に成ったみたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.33,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Kozue, you seem off.{NOTE:こうぜ、すこし変よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:56.79,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,What's wrong?{NOTE:どうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:58.50,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Do you feel unwell?{NOTE:どこか具合でも悪いんじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.{NOTE:ん、大丈夫。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:02.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It feels a bit unreal that I'm here in America.{NOTE:きっと夢にまで見たアメリカ(XX・へ来て)のぼせちゃったのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:03.68,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I see.{NOTE:そうならいいけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:07.39,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! There are hippies in front of our hotel now!{NOTE:ちょっと、ちょっと今ホテルの前をヒッピーが歩いてんのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.52,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,Real hippies! Wanna go see them?{NOTE:本間のヒッピーやで。見に行きませんか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.27,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Kozue, let's go check them out.{NOTE:こずえ、言ってみましょうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:14.56,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Nah, I'll pass. I'm a little tired.{NOTE:ん、ごめんなさい。私ちょっと疲れてるから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:16.52,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,All right. I'll go though.{NOTE:そ？じゃ、私は行ってくるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:17.52,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,Hurry up!{NOTE:はいよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:48.01,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Nobody, not even coach Inokuma, knows what's ahead.{NOTE:誰も。猪野熊先生だって知らないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:49.26,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What should I do?{NOTE:どうしよう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:53.02,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Shellenina's cross toss. Borchinskaya's killer spike.{NOTE:シェレーニナの十字トスを、ボルチンスカヤの殺人スパイクを…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:54.35,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,How do we defeat it?{NOTE:どうしたらいいの？}
Comment: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:02.99,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:08.37,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Wait here.{NOTE:皆はここで待てろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:13.75,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– They're Czechoslovakia's team.\N– Wow, they're so tall.{NOTE:チェコの選手だわ。わ、皆大きいのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.16,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,They must be powerful.{NOTE:力もありそうだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:22.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Oh?{NOTE:お？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.13,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:暫く鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:え、暫く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:27.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Shellenina.{NOTE:シェレーニナ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:29.47,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I'm glad we got to meet again.{NOTE:又会えてとても嬉しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:35.64,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I was sure that I'd bump into you here.{NOTE:私鮎原はきっとここへ遣ってくると思っていました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.85,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,Who is she?{NOTE:誰、あの人？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:39.44,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,It's the captain of the Soviet team we played against before.{NOTE:以前私達の戦ったソ連のキャプテンだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:41.73,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,She has intimidating aura around her.{NOTE:見ただけで威圧感感じるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:44.94,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Last time we played with them,\Nwe felt like children in the dark.{NOTE:私達その時丸で子供のようにあしらわれたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:15.85,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I am really excited to see how far you progressed by now.{NOTE:あれからのあなたの進歩。私楽しみにしてるのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:19.48,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,Shellenina!{NOTE:シェレーニナ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:20.65,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Ah, Cassie!{NOTE:あ、キャシー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.32,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Ayuhara, let me introduce you.{NOTE:鮎原、紹介しましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:27.49,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,She's American team's captain, Cassie.{NOTE:アメリカチームのキャプテン、キャシー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.78,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,Ah, All-Japan's team.{NOTE:お、オールジャパン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:31.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm Ayuhara Kozue.{NOTE:鮎原こずえです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.20,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.{NOTE:よろしく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:33.70,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,How do you do?{NOTE:How do you do?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.62,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– I'm Tom. Nice to meet you.\N– Hello.{NOTE:—トムです。よろしく。\\N—よろしく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:39.00,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,I have been to Japan once.{NOTE:僕日本へ行ったことがあります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.42,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,Japan is a wonderful country.{NOTE:日本の国素晴らしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:43.96,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I played with both Ayuhara and Cassie before.{NOTE:私鮎原ともキャシーとも試合しました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:48.09,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I think that your attack and Cassie's attack are both very remarkable.{NOTE:あなたのアタック、キャシーのアタック、どちらも素晴らしいと思いました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:56.35,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,Then the strength between you two could be said to be fifty-fifty.{NOTE:それでは二人の実力はfifty-fiftyですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:57.39,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:15:01.19,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,United States were second in last year's world championship.{NOTE:アメリカは去年の世界選手権で二位でした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:06.78,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,We had a hard time playing against Cassie's team's fast and unpredictable attacks.{NOTE:私達はキャシー達のリズムのある境界の攻撃に大変苦戦したのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:11.99,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,The Soviet Union who led us by our noses had a hard time?{NOTE:私達を手玉にとったソ連が苦戦したいって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:13.66,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,Yes. Don't you think so, Tom?{NOTE:Yes, don't you think so, Tom?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:14.95,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,Ah, haha.{NOTE:あ、ハハハ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:24.25,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,We're short of time regarding the gym usage, so we decided on the order of practice.{NOTE:練習場は過酷時間制になってるから、練習も順番だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:25.63,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Kenya, Korea.{NOTE:ケニア、韓国。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.21,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,After them it's our turn.{NOTE:その次は日本だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:31.93,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Make sure to closely observe the other teams while waiting for our turn.{NOTE:順番を待つあいだに他国チームの技術をよーく見ておくのもと一緒のうちだぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:35.60,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Ah, that's…{NOTE:あ、あれは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.15,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,Awesome power.{NOTE:すごいパワーだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.27,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,They must weight very little.{NOTE:XXXみたいに体が軽いのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:50.86,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,We didn't think anything about the other teams.{NOTE:全然考えてもいなかったチームだって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:53.36,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,We dropped the ball in that regard.{NOTE:私達勉強不足だったよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:55.70,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,And now we're facing teams from all over the world.{NOTE:今やっと世界に挑戦が分かったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:59.25,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I am a little worried what kind of teams we'll bump into.{NOTE:XXXどんなチームが出てくるか？ちょっと心配に成ってきた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:04.63,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,They're rather unrefined in their technique.{NOTE:ばってん技術的にはまだ荒削りなことだとよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:08.80,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,It's changing.{NOTE:交代だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.13,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,Next is Korea if I recall.{NOTE:次は韓国じゃね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:23.69,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,She throws them pretty hard, don't you think?{NOTE:あれ？あのボール投げてのXXXじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:25.94,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,She must be their captain.{NOTE:韓国のキャプテンよね、きっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.61,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,She's like a machine gun.{NOTE:丸で機関銃見たいね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.73,Default,Noda,0,0,0,,I'm impressed.{NOTE:驚いたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.32,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Perfect receiving.{NOTE:完璧なレシーブ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:33.99,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,They don't drop a single ball.{NOTE:一つも落とさないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:36.32,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,It's not just receiving.{NOTE:レシーブだけじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:38.74,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,It's serving, too.{NOTE:サーブも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:40.95,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,Tosses, too.{NOTE:トスも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.41,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,And also spikes.{NOTE:そしてスパイクも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:46.33,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Everyone is at the same level and plays flawlessly.{NOTE:全てに斑なくどの選手も卒なく遣ってるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:50.00,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,But in exchange, they don't seem to possess any special techniques.{NOTE:ま、その代わり、得に決め技も出ない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:52.34,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,They don't have revolving receive nor falling leaf.{NOTE:回転レシーブも木の葉落としもない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:55.47,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,They've only focused on polishing standard techniques.{NOTE:皆スタンダードの技術が磨き抜かれているだけだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:58.18,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,But it seems to have motivated the girls.{NOTE:だが、皆にはXX刺激になっているようだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:16:59.01,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Heh.{NOTE:へへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.18,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,It is a good lesson.{NOTE:いい勉強だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:05.56,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I've been only thinking about\Nthe Soviet Union until now.{NOTE:今までソ連ソ連とソ連の事ばかりしか考えていなかったけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:09.15,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But will we stand up against the other teams until we get to play with the Russians?{NOTE:ソ連と戦うまでXX勝っていけるだろうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.86,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Then there are United States who won second place last year.{NOTE:それと去年準優勝したアメリカ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:16.95,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Ah, they're here.\N– How nice.{NOTE:—Ah, XXX.\\N—How nice.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:20.79,Alternative,Alternative,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of attack do they have under their disposal.{NOTE:いつもなる軽快な攻撃ってどんなものかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:21.70,Default,Ootsuki,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.00,Default,Ootsuki,0,0,0,,I feel less and less sure.{NOTE:だんだん自身が無くなってくみたいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:26.46,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's no good.{NOTE:行けない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:31.30,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,As their captain, I should encourage them somehow.{NOTE:キャプテンの私からこんなことでは何とか皆を力付けなくちゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:32.80,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But…{NOTE:でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.26,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But…!{NOTE:でも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:35.88,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Alright, it's our turn.{NOTE:さ、我々の番だぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:36.93,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,– Yes sir.\N– Yes sir.{NOTE:—はい。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:42.31,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're thinking about a lot of things after coming here to New York.{NOTE:ニューヨークへ来てからお前たちも色々と感じたものがあると思う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:44.06,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,The Soviets aren't our only enemies.{NOTE:ソ連ばかりが敵ではないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:46.35,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,There are lots of other formidable enemies.{NOTE:他にも強敵がいくらでもいる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:48.94,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Focus fully on the enemy that stands before you.{NOTE:目の前にいる相手の事を忘れない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:50.15,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,– Yes sir.\N– Yes sir.{NOTE:—はい。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:51.44,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Okay, time to practice.{NOTE:さ、練習だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.61,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,Finally it is Japan team. Take a good look.{NOTE:いよいよ日本チームだ。よく見ておくんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:58.11,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Here we go, Ayuhara!{NOTE:さ、行くぞ。鮎原！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah, damn!{NOTE:あ、行けない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:07.54,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,What's wrong?{NOTE:どうした！？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:10.50,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's no good.{NOTE:行けない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.50,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,What's that?{NOTE:何だ何だ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.13,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,What's with your form?{NOTE:どいつもこいつも足るんでるぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:19.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!{NOTE:な、何て事なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:21.60,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,Oh!{NOTE:お！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.39,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,What's the matter?{NOTE:どうしたのか、これは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:27.02,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,Shellenina, what's this? Surely that's not the extent of Japanese skill?{NOTE:シェレーニナ、どうだ？あれが日本の実力とは思わないが、どうだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:28.35,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Strange.{NOTE:可笑しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.02,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I'm puzzled.{NOTE:何が迷ってる感じ出す。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.61,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Spike! Kakinouchi, you first!{NOTE:スパイク！垣之内から！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:39.91,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Sanjou, your turn!{NOTE:次三条！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:46.08,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Not good! Everyone's nervous!{NOTE:行けない！皆が動揺してる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:01.93,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,If things continue like this and we end up losing the first round…{NOTE:もし、もしも第一選で負けるような事がなったら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:03.97,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,…I can't return to Japan.{NOTE:私とても日本にか帰らないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.23,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I didn't see that coming.{NOTE:ちょっとショックだったわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:13.56,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Things went down surprisingly, but I still think it'll be all right.{NOTE:予想じゃそれ以外問題にもしてなかったけど、でも大丈夫よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:15.27,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,We'll overcome it somehow.{NOTE:何とか遣れるわ、きっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:19.36,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,Yep. I didn't feel very well today. There's nothing to worry about.{NOTE:そうよ。今日は皆調子が出へんかったけど、心配することあらへん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:21.45,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,We'll regain our form in no time.{NOTE:試合までにXX調子を取り戻すだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:26.79,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,Ah, finally at hotel.{NOTE:あ、着いた着いた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.95,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– I'm hungry.\N– Let's check out the city after we eat.{NOTE:—お腹が空いた。\\N—ご飯食べたら町へ行きXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:29.46,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.92,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:32.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Do you need anything?{NOTE:何か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:37.71,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, Cassie wants to invite you and the Japanese team to a party.{NOTE:鮎原さん、キャシーがあなた達日本チームパーティーに招待したいと申しております。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:38.51,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:39.47,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Party?{NOTE:パーティー？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:40.22,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,That's right.{NOTE:そうです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.01,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,Please come by all means.{NOTE:是非来てくださいね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:46.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Thanks for the invitation. However, I have to consult it with our coach before I can reply.{NOTE:それはどうも。でも、コーチに相談しなければ、お返事出来ませんけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:47.60,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,Hi!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:51.69,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,Ah, Cassie said she'd be really thrilled to see you come over.{NOTE:あは、キャシーあなた達の御出でを心から待っていると言ってます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Cassie.{NOTE:キャシー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.52,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,Come on, Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:どうぞ、鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:59.94,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Kozue, we can't refuse her after\Nshe went through the trouble to invite us.{NOTE:こずえ、折角招待されたのに断るってことないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:02.61,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,A real party! That's great!{NOTE:本場のパーティー何て素敵じゃないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:04.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But we have a game tomorrow.{NOTE:ん、でも明日は試合よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:06.99,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I don't think it's best time to be partying.{NOTE:パーティー所じゃないと思うんだけどな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:09.75,Default,Mishima,0,0,0,,That's right. We didn't fly here to party.{NOTE:そうよ。私達はパーティーに来たんじゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:14.04,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,I oppose to it too. We should do it when we have more free time.{NOTE:内も反対。そんな暇があるなら、XXX方がいいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:17.42,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,But it's our chance to know the life of an American middle school student.{NOTE:でもアメリカの中学生の生活を知るチャンスでもあるし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.42,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:19.63,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Ayuhara.\N– Sir.{NOTE:—鮎原。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:22.80,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,I'm going to a preparatory meeting\Nfor tomorrow's game.{NOTE:これから試合の打ち合わせがあるんでいってくるから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:23.30,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yes sir.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah, uhm, coach…{NOTE:あ、あのコーチ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:25.43,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,What is it?{NOTE:何だ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:29.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Actually, we were invited to a party from the American team.{NOTE:実はあの、アメリカチームからパーティーに招待されたんですけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:32.27,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Decisions about such matters are up to you, the captain.{NOTE:そんな事はキャプテンのお前が決める事だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:36.73,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Lovely, professor Inokuma's understanding.{NOTE:素敵、猪野熊先生話せるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:38.07,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.{NOTE:ね、行こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:55.33,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,Welcome. We've been waiting for you eagerly.{NOTE:あ、ようこそ。首を長くして待っていましたよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:56.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Thank you for the invitation.{NOTE:ご招待有難う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:59.84,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,Ah, you came after all! I'm really glad.{NOTE:あ、明日来ました。私とても嬉しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:02.09,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,Americans are pretty open, aren't they?{NOTE:開けっぴろげね、アメリカ人って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.93,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,Hey, let's welcome them!{NOTE:はい、皆いらっしゃい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:06.80,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,They're the Japanese wonder girls!{NOTE:こちら日本の魔女！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.10,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Hi!{NOTE:Hi!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.85,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,They're the All-America team members.{NOTE:オールアメリカのメンバー達さ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.43,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,Make yourself at home. Take a seat.{NOTE:ささどうぞどうぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:18.23,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, let me have this dance.{NOTE:鮎原さんお願いします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:20.23,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah, no, I'm bad at da—{NOTE:あ、だ、だめよ私何か。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:22.28,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,Come on, dance with him, captain.{NOTE:踊りなさいよキャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:23.94,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Yeah. Don't be party pooper.{NOTE:そうよそうよ。踊りなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:32.33,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Let's dance too.{NOTE:さ私達も踊ろうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:32.95,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:35.92,Default,Miyatsu,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm hungry.{NOTE:XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:38.50,Default,Miyatsu,0,0,0,,I have to eat something first.{NOTE:XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:40.46,Default,Miyatsu,0,0,0,,Ah, delicious.{NOTE:ん、上手いっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:43.13,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Come on.\N– No no, I can't dance.{NOTE:—どうぞどうぞ。\\N—行けない行けない。内踊れないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:48.18,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,How is it, Kozue? It was a good call, don't you think?{NOTE:どうこずえ？やっぱり来てよかったでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:49.51,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:57.85,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What cheerful people.{NOTE:何て陽気な人達だろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:21:58.85,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I know.{NOTE:そうだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:22:00.52,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Maybe that's how it should be.{NOTE:これでいいのかもしれない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:04.36,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We might have the game tomorrow, but nothing good will come of it if we overthink it.{NOTE:試合は明日からだけど、いつまでくよくよと考えたって始まらないもん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.82,0:22:13.37,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Coach Inokuma didn't really oppose to this party.{NOTE:猪野熊コーチがこのパーティーに出ることに反対しなかったのも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.37,0:22:18.87,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,He must have known we're nervous and wanted us to relax a bit.{NOTE:きっと緊張しすぎて自信とサイトを無くしかけている私達をリラックスさせるためだったんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.87,0:22:19.79,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.00,0:22:22.50,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,I got a call just now.{NOTE:今連絡ありました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:25.09,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,The first game is United States vs. Japan.{NOTE:明日の試合アメリカと日本が戦います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:40.15,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,All right, everyone. Let's make a toast for the match between Japan and America tomorrow.{NOTE:さ、皆さん。明日の日本とアメリカの試合のために乾杯しましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:41.86,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,Everyone together.{NOTE:皆さん、ご一緒に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.40,0:22:46.40,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Cheers.\N– Cheers.{NOTE:—乾杯。\\N—乾杯。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.44,0:22:48.78,Alternative,Cassie,0,0,0,,Ayuhara.{NOTE:鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:52.53,Alternative,Cassie,0,0,0,,Last year, United States' team was second in the world.{NOTE:アメリカに去年の世界選手権で二位でした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:58.25,Alternative,Shellenina,0,0,0,,We had a hard time playing against Cassie's team's fast and unpredictable attacks.{NOTE:私達はキャシー達のリズムのある境界の攻撃に大変苦戦したのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.17,0:23:03.34,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,Let's do our best.{NOTE:ベストを尽くして戦いましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.34,0:23:05.21,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,– Yeah!\N– Yeah!{NOTE:—おう！\\N—おう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:18.35,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,If I show a sign of weakness, it's our defeat.{NOTE:弱きを起こしたら負けたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:21.40,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We've came to the America on behalf of the Japanese nation.{NOTE:私達は日本人の血も代表してアメリカに来ているのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.40,0:23:24.27,Alternative,Reporter A,0,0,0,,– Can you really win?\N– Your opponents are strong.{NOTE:—勝てる？大丈夫？\\N—敵も強いよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:25.44,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We will win.{NOTE:勝つわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:26.73,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We will definitely win.{NOTE:絶対に勝つわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:33.28,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I swear by the red sun like Midori in the Haneda airport that we will win.{NOTE:私は…私はあの羽田の日の丸にかけて改めて誓うわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:37.62,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We'll show them what we're made of and demonstrate a splendid victory.{NOTE:新手も全力を尽くして戦うとそして必ず勝つと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.62,0:23:39.75,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Both with USA and USSR.{NOTE:ソ連にも、アメリカにも。}
Comment: 0,0:23:56.43,0:23:56.43,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:04.52,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,At last, the curtain of the World Junior Volleyball Championship is unveiled.{NOTE:ついに世界ジュニアバレーボール選手権大会の幕は切って落とされた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.52,0:24:07.11,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,The long and hard training of All-Japan's team…{NOTE:オールジャパンの長く苦しい特訓も…}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:09.53,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,…was all for today's sake.{NOTE:…全て今日のためにやったのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.53,0:24:15.16,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Starting from Midori's serve, the battle they have bet their youth on…{NOTE:そしてこのみどりの打つサーブから彼女達の青春をバレーボールに賭けた戦いが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.16,0:24:19.62,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,…aiming for victory and glory, is on.{NOTE:…勝利と栄光をめざして今まさに始まろうとしている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.62,0:24:22.87,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Please look forward to the next episode.{NOTE:次回アタックナンバーワンにご期待ください。}
